name: To Øl Gift Card
description: We have your gifting needs covered with our digital-only gift cards, the perfect gift for anyone but especially that special someone. NOTE: These gift cards can only be used on the To Øl webshop. The cards are sent by email and are not a physical product.

name: Implosion Bundle
description: The Implosion Bundle gives you all the whole range of our award-winning alcohol free beer, offered for a special low price. It's all flavors but without the kick — whether you want a crisp, refreshing taste or a fruity flavor, this bundle got you covered. The bundle includes following:2x Implosion - 22 DKK value, 33 cl

name: Implosion Pink Sour
description: This is a non-alcoholic kettle soured beer flavored with lychee and hibiscus. Hopped with loral and ekuanot to play up the floral nature of the lychee, and pink from hibiscus and purple carrot.

name: Implosion Amber Lager
description: Malt-forward amber lager that doesn't taste like a compromise. Loosely based on our Driving Home from Xmas, which was itself loosely based on the 45 Days Vienna Lager — this is a malt-forward beer with a good amount of Vienna and Munich malts doing the work. A hint of Czech Saaz and Mittelfrüh hops give a light herbal/

name: Implosion Fruited
description: This is a fruited non-alcoholic beer. It is different from the Lowmotion series in that it is not soured. But the raspberry/elderflower blend gives a nice, sessionable and refreshing experience that won't get you buzzed. We hopped it very lightly so that the main flavor to focus on is the fruit.

name: Implosion — Alcohol Free Lager
description: Introducing our latest non-alcoholic beer crafted for those who seek the authentic taste of a clean lager without the alcohol. name: Implosion — Alcohol Free Beer
description: Enjoy this delicious non-alcoholic beer with all its complexity, crispness & flavor while keeping a level head! It is light and chuggable, with nice peachy notes from the yeast. Slightly sweet, but not too prominent, nice and fresh hop aromas, and absolutely NO hangover! Alcohol-free beer as it should be.
